<div class="com-share" data-id="20883" data-title="《沃尔玛全球关店269家，中国怎么还在开？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/20883/medium/20883.jpg?1453107580" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/20883.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
